Feature: Landing page management
  The User have permission update landing page will be able to update
  the content in landing page

  Background:
    Given a administrator named "Admin"
    And role of "Admin" is ADMIN
    And this user have permission update landing page
    And a customer named "User"
    And role of "User" is USER
    And this user haven't permission update landing page

  Scenario: Admin update content in landing page
    Given I am logged in as Admin
    When I try to update content in landing page
    Then I should see "Success, Updated Landing page successfuly."

  Scenario: User update content in landing pae
    Given I am logged in as User
    Given I am logged in as User
    When I try to update content in landing page
    Then I should see "Failure, Access denied."